	<title>I. Entrée solennelle de Jésus à Jérusalem, le Dimanche des Rameaux.</title>
	<subtitle><bible><ss>Mt</ss> <sc>21</sc>.<sv>1–11</sv></bible>. Parall. <bible><ss>Mc</ss> <sc>11</sc>.<sv>1-11</sv></bible> ; <bible><ss>Lc</ss> <sc>19</sc>.<sv>29-44</sv></bible> ; <bible><ss>Jn</ss> <sc>12</sc>.<sv>12-19</sv></bible>.</subtitle>
